---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Agentic Thinking"
  description="About Agentic Thinking — a blog exploring AI agents and autonomous systems."
>
  <div class="prose mx-auto">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>
      <strong>Agentic Thinking</strong> is a blog exploring the rapidly evolving world of AI agents,
      autonomous systems, and agentic workflows. We cover topics like multi-agent architectures,
      tool-using LLMs, agent frameworks, and the practical realities of building and deploying agents.
    </p>
    <p>
      Whether you're a developer building your first agent pipeline or an architect designing
      enterprise-scale autonomous systems, there's something here for you.
    </p>
    <h2>Topics</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>AI agent frameworks and architectures</li>
      <li>Autonomous workflow design</li>
      <li>Tool use and function calling</li>
      <li>Multi-agent coordination</li>
      <li>Evaluation and safety for agents</li>
      <li>Practical implementation guides</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
